name: SAP EXTERNAL Fiori Web Stencils v1.96
description:
The original SAP Fiori user interface for web apps based on the SAPUI5 framework. Design engaging and intuitive apps that can run on any device. You can use this stencil set to create high-fidelity SAP Fiori designs.

This is from SAP Design System website: https://experience.sap.com/fiori-design-web/
